actions.text: Committee on Veterans. Original measure reported to Senate by Senator Murkowski. Without written report.
Referred to the Committee on Budget.
Committee on Budget. Approved for reporting without amendment favorably.
Committee on Budget. Reported to Senate by Senator Domenici without amendment and with a preamble. Without written report.
Placed on Senate Legislative Calendar under General Orders. Calendar No. 241.

official_title: An original resolution providing for the waiver of section 303(a) of the Congressional Budget Act of 1974 with respect to H.R.752, as reported by the Senate Committee on Veterans' Affairs.

summary.text: Waives certain requirements of the Congressional Budget Act of 1974 with respect to the consideration of H.R. 752 (veterans' educational assistance).
